post_desc: Even though my papa doesn't celebrate Easter we're still wishing everybody a happy Easter! #misspeaches

Great news everybody! I'm back home from the vet/summer camp! I feel great! Thank you to @Veterinary Emergency Group for taking such good care of me. I'm so happy to be home with my papa!!! No more gum for me! #misspeaches
I may book my next vacation to this vet hospital. It’s 5 star service all the way. Way nicer than the Tampa Edition. @Veterinary Emergency Group #misspeaches

Good news everybody! I feel great and Papa said I can stay at the hospital for an extra night for sleep away camp! (My Papa said it’s because they need to observe me just to be safe) Everybody at Veterinary Emergency Group is so nice! Eating that toxic Ice Breakers gum ended up being so much fun! Don’t tell Papa I said that! He said the makers of Ice Breakers Gum should be in prison! #misspeaches
I’m making the most of this sleepover camp #misspeaches
1:30am update. All my vitals are good. My papa said I can have unlimited pup cups when I get home. No more gum though. #misspeaches

So umm I ate a ton of icebreakers gum tonight and my Papa rushed me to the ER. Apparently gum is extremely poisonous for dogs. Big gum should be in jail. Anyway they made me throw it up and told my papa they have to hold me for observation. My Papa started crying. I told him to be brave and that I’ll be fine. It’s kind of like going to summer camp. #misspeaches
Um hello? Im down here! I think these people got confused. Why are they people taking pictures of my papa and not me? #misspeaches
I went shopping at @ChanelOfficial today with Papa. It was exhausting. #misspeaches
I don’t have the heart to tell my Papa he’s an awful singer #misspeaches
Hello, I’m Miss Peaches! If you see me in the street please say hello to me. I like saying hi. #misspeaches
I'm so happy my papa @Dave Portnoy is home from his business trip! I missed him so much! #misspeaches
My Papa says no more eating hats because it can make my belly hurt.  But I like eating hats!! #misspeaches
I miss you too Papa!! #misspeaches
I miss you too Papa!! #misspeaches
Custom Poems By Jenna wrote a poem for me and my Papa! We read it together and I think I saw my Papa cry but he said it was just allergies. #misspeaches
There is a maniac Frenchie loose in my neighborhood! #misspeaches

When my papa 1st pick me up I didn’t know how to chase a ball or play at all but now playing is one of my favorite things to do! I even learned how to run after a ball! I love playing with my papa because he gets very excited whenever he sees me run and I like making papa happy! #misspeaches
If my papa didn’t want me to eat his sunglasses why did he keep putting them back in the same spot? I’m sorry papa but not sorry! #misspeaches

My Papa and I met the Easter Bunny today! I had a great time meeting everybody! My Papa says I’m a star! You can get your pet photos at Dadeland Mall 3/21 and 3/25. Thank you to @dadelandmall for donating 10k to an animal rescue/shelter charity of Miss Peaches choice!
I love mornings with my papa! #misspeaches
I took my first boat ride with my Papa today! It was fun! I’d do it again! PS- feel free to send this to my past owner and tell them screw you! Peaches is doing just fine thank you very much!

My Papa and I are proud to announce we raised another 100k for dog rescues/charities. 25k each has been given to @New York Bully Crew, @TFPRM, @PawPatrolAnimalRescue & @MuttyPawsRescueinc. We’ve raised almost 400k so far. As a reminder every penny we make will be donated. I have new gear that just went on sale today. Save all the dogs! #adoptdontshop
It’s hot in sunny Florida today. A gal needs to stay cool! #misspeaches
Papa I’m snoozing! #misspeaches
Time to get up Papa! #misspeaches
This message is from my papa and I.  Please no more gifts.  While we certainly appreciate it I have all the gifts I could ever want.  #misspeaches
I love watching the sunrise in the morning from bed! It makes me appreciate life! #misspeaches
Good morning everybody! I love watching the sunrise #misspeaches
I had my first photo shoot for Time Out Miami today! Papa said I killed it! #misspeaches

My favorite thing to do is make new friends! #misspeaches

My Papa doesn’t understand that I want to walk until I get tired so he needs to pull the empty wagon and walk me at the same time until I’m ready to be pulled in it. #MissPeaches
My papa always has my back! ❤️❤️❤️❤️ Thank you Papa! #misspeaches
My Papa took me shopping today. I can’t wait to go again! #misspeaches
